Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.09,0:02:36.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马尔克希亚斯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.22,0:02:38.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不觉得变的好玩起来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.48,0:02:41.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊  好久没试过这样全力一战了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.46,0:02:45.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放手干吧  我美丽的酒杯——玛裘莉·顿
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.50,0:03:02.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「顶之座」——赫卡特
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.42,0:03:05.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,率领「化装舞会」的其中一人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.70,0:03:08.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是谁都无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.41,0:03:12.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快把悠二还给我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.08,0:03:30.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.53,0:03:33.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是我的人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.58,0:03:37.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为容器已经结合了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.66,0:04:09.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来她就是被这庞大的存在之力所充满的机关的核心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.02,0:04:12.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打倒她就能停止了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.01,0:04:33.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那样的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.97,0:04:45.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然除了阻止「顶之座」以外别无他法
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.49,0:04:50.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必须尽快  这样下去城市会崩坏也说不定
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.10,0:04:55.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  该怎么做
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.08,0:04:59.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,御崎市会…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.78,0:05:05.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行…得做些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.21,0:05:10.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的思念正充满着我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.20,0:05:13.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至今以来不知结合了多少容器
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.20,0:05:18.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算把欲望全部吞噬也未曾得到的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.94,0:05:21.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.50,0:05:44.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思  到此为止了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.95,0:05:51.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必须要去赫卡特那了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.01,0:05:58.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再陪我打一会是也
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.43,0:05:59.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,继续战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.15,0:06:03.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真缠人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.68,0:06:35.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,切…燃料过多也挺麻烦的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.71,0:06:38.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊  看来会永远打下去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.03,0:06:42.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「千变」啊  这难道不是你们的目的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.05,0:06:47.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只要…我的赫卡特能满足就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.09,0:06:49.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咳…变态的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.35,0:06:51.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是玩人偶的料吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.26,0:07:00.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发生了什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.37,0:07:03.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  看那
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.92,0:07:07.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什…什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.25,0:07:15.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没问题  一定能回来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.47,0:07:22.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对的  坂井同学和小缘一定会回来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.59,0:07:30.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全不能靠近
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.55,0:07:32.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要把坂井悠二从那里放出来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.68,0:07:35.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要把零时迷子分离
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.78,0:07:37.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有的都应该会停止
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.74,0:07:39.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,试试看
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.61,0:07:49.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你用我的记忆和思念来充满自己
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.52,0:07:52.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样就满足了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.16,0:07:54.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直在追寻着
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.24,0:07:56.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祈祷着
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.38,0:07:58.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.90,0:07:59.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.08,0:08:04.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,触摸到你的时候终于明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.14,0:08:07.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我追寻着的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.82,0:08:08.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.23,0:08:10.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并不是单纯的火雾战士
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.00,0:08:13.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不是单纯的火炬
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.82,0:08:14.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是坂井悠二
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.97,0:08:19.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.80,0:08:24.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我所追寻的是…我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.55,0:08:28.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真实存在着的…我自己
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.39,0:08:31.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确实…容器最初重合的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.56,0:08:34.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是空无一物的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.05,0:08:36.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在…不对
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.68,0:08:41.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我如此得被填满着
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.96,0:08:42.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.91,0:08:44.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在是我的回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.76,0:08:46.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.74,0:08:49.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算用别人的回忆来填满自己
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.01,0:08:51.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是毫无意义的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.64,0:08:52.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的你并不是你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.70,0:08:58.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是作为火炬的你不也被坂井悠二的回忆所充满着吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.34,0:09:06.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以  与夏娜相遇的我果然只是个单纯的火炬而已
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.92,0:09:11.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…但现在
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.16,0:09:14.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悠二
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.76,0:09:19.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在不同了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.41,0:09:22.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从那时就一直在思考着  苦恼着
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.97,0:09:24.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回想起来的那些都是我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.48,0:09:28.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以再明确地说一次
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.53,0:09:36.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是坂井悠二
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.49,0:09:38.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.80,0:09:40.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只属于你的自己究竟在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.21,0:09:49.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.33,0:10:23.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悠二
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.78,0:10:26.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你由我来守护
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.73,0:10:53.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.38,0:10:55.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悠二
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.57,0:10:57.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.21,0:11:16.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,填满我的东西…消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.81,0:11:17.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.32,0:11:20.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可能会被我的回忆填满呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.40,0:11:23.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你从一开始就始终空无一物
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.82,0:12:21.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.71,0:12:34.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.97,0:12:38.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.07,0:12:41.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉  都是因为我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.19,0:12:46.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为…有人拜托我要带你回去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.63,0:12:47.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.39,0:12:52.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那两个人和…吉田一美
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.38,0:12:55.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.86,0:12:57.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都在担心我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.69,0:12:58.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.52,0:13:01.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  最想这么做的是我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.52,0:13:03.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.97,0:13:15.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你从一开始就始终空无一物
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.62,0:13:28.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赫卡特
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.94,0:13:34.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  不是说好不能中途退出的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.55,0:13:41.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.95,0:13:44.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.82,0:13:45.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,异常事态
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.94,0:13:51.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.89,0:13:56.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「顶之座」正在将吞噬了的存在之力释放出来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.00,0:14:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过这量…真是恐怖的容器
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.47,0:14:02.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,城市呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.30,0:14:17.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,城市…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.02,0:14:21.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如此庞大的存在之力回流的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.67,0:14:24.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恐怕已经没空等着自然恢复了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.89,0:14:26.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.83,0:14:35.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多么精彩的情况
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.25,0:14:36.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幻觉还是现实
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.80,0:14:38.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是超越了世界所能承受界限的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.90,0:14:41.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,存在之力的饱和
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.88,0:14:44.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会变成什么样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.45,0:14:47.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是待会要确认的！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.49,0:14:53.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是时候了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.46,0:14:59.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有唯一的手段
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.91,0:15:00.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.09,0:15:01.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.76,0:15:08.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「天壤劫火」亚拉斯托尔的显现
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.90,0:15:11.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,显现？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.06,0:15:14.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是让亚拉斯托尔出现在这个世界
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.46,0:15:17.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作为红世魔人的我的显现
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.44,0:15:20.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会消耗大量的存在之力
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.90,0:15:27.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要使用现在饱和的庞大存在之力来显现的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.72,0:15:30.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,估计城市崩坏也会停止
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.79,0:15:31.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.97,0:15:34.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  如果我显现的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.12,0:15:37.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作为容器的火雾战士也会被破坏
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.88,0:15:40.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,曾经便是如此…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.65,0:15:43.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,破坏是指…难道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.62,0:15:46.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对…会死
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.69,0:15:51.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是炎发灼眼的火雾战士被赐予的宿命
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.86,0:15:57.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我全明白了这些才和亚拉斯托尔订下契约的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.49,0:16:07.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有不好的预感是也
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.56,0:16:08.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,急速前进
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.41,0:16:11.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我作为夏娜救了悠二
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.20,0:16:15.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次要作为火雾战士来完成使命
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.24,0:16:18.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是我…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.47,0:16:20.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.82,0:16:24.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坂井悠二
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.72,0:16:29.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经没时间带你逃走了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.03,0:16:37.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.14,0:16:40.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我早就决定了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.11,0:16:42.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和夏娜一起走
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.92,0:16:44.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这份心情现在也没变
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.85,0:16:46.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悠二
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.84,0:17:08.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天破壤碎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.67,0:17:22.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…喜欢悠二
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.04,0:17:31.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.31,0:17:32.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天破壤碎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.20,0:17:53.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,NO  难得的饱和状态啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.39,0:17:56.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没办法了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.02,0:17:58.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,脱出
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.02,0:17:59.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.25,0:18:01.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要着手准备下一个实验了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.55,0:18:04.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又来了啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.19,0:18:23.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.24,0:18:24.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想死吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.34,0:18:25.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快走
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.37,0:18:29.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被「天壤劫火」吞没的话就完了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.06,0:18:48.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…什么也没有
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.86,0:18:51.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系的  赫卡特
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.85,0:18:54.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就是你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.00,0:19:31.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小鬼…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.52,0:20:05.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.09,0:20:06.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏娜…来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.59,0:20:10.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.72,0:20:11.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.84,0:20:13.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悠二
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.12,0:20:14.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.89,0:20:15.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快起来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.23,0:20:17.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,起来？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.77,0:20:18.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是已经…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.85,0:20:22.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.12,0:20:23.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.04,0:20:28.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.53,0:20:31.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我为什么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.65,0:20:36.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的容器容纳了我的全部存在
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.13,0:20:40.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然订契约的时候我已经感觉到大小了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.66,0:20:42.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么说来  以后随时都可以出来了？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.33,0:20:48.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别说傻话  赌上生命的行为怎么能一再尝试啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.91,0:20:53.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我原来还活着啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.54,0:20:55.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.69,0:20:56.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也总算活着
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.55,0:21:03.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悠二
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.22,0:21:17.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个掉了…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.71,0:21:25.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看到了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.78,0:21:26.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.88,0:21:27.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.85,0:21:28.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说了没看到
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.33,0:21:30.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你干嘛看别的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.90,0:21:31.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.60,0:21:32.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别看…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.84,0:21:34.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还不是夏娜你…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.02,0:21:35.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吵死了  吵死了  吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.35,0:21:49.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,失礼了是也
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.56,0:21:55.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,威尔艾米娜
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.51,0:22:06.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还真是走狗屎运啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.58,0:22:08.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有资格说别人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.90,0:22:09.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.59,0:22:10.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那  准备怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.43,0:22:13.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍微离开下就这副德行了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.05,0:22:15.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.54,0:22:17.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再照看下好了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.25,0:22:25.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,转啊转
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.03,0:22:27.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  别转了喂
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.24,0:22:28.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,救命啊  两位
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.23,0:22:30.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.42,0:22:31.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大姐说暂时待在这
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.50,0:22:34.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不知道好还是不好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.33,0:22:35.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干嘛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.77,0:22:37.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就不能坦率一点吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.82,0:23:00.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,路上小心
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.04,0:23:03.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏娜  今天晚饭会准备好吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.74,0:23:04.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定要来哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.80,0:23:29.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哟…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.15,0:23:31.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早…早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.86,0:23:37.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.47,0:23:42.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第二学期胜负会分晓也说不定
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.57,0:23:48.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下啊  池
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.36,0:23:54.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会输的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.67,0:23:57.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为今天第二回合开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.56,0:23:59.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.54,0:24:02.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,带悠二回来的时候还哭着道谢的说
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.26,0:24:04.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以说那是第一回合
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.63,0:24:07.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,彼此加油吧  夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.09,0:24:11.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不会输的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.89,0:24:12.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定不会输
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.40,0:24:23.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们将来也会一成不变的前进
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.67,0:24:27.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直到在世界脱轨之前
